.Dd NOVEMBER 23, 2009
.Dt MAN2MEDIAWIKI 1
.Os
.ds vT BSDBuild Reference
.ds oS BSDBuild 1.0
.Sh NAME
.Nm man2mediawiki
.Nd Generate MediaWiki articles from manual pages
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm man2mediawiki
.Op Fl u username
.Op Ar category
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
tool uses formatted manual page source as generated by
.Xr man2wiki 1
to generate (and update) a category of MediaWiki articles (via
.Xr MediaWiki::API 3 ) .
.Pp
.Pp
The options are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl u
Specify username to log in to the wiki.
The password will be asked interactively and stored in
.Pa ~/.man2mediawiki .
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr man2wiki 1 ,
.Xr MediaWiki::API 3 ,
.Xr build.man.mk 5 ,
.Xr build.common.mk 5
